<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="first-adv">first <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /fɜːst/    美 /fɜːrst/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-firstly-first-of-all">1.★ <strong>最先；首次；[句子副词] 第一 (firstly / first of all)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Who <strong>came first</strong> in the race?
比赛中谁跑了第一？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>First I want to talk about wildlife protection.
首先我想谈谈野生动植物的保护问题。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="at-first">at first</h3>
<p>1.<strong>起先；开始的时候：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I didn't like the job much at first.
起初我并不太喜欢这个工作。</p></div>

<h3 id="first-of-all">first of all</h3>
<p>1.<strong>首先；第一 (first / firstly)：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I don't think Helen should go — first of all, she is too young.
我认为海伦不应该去，首先，她太年轻了。</p></div></div>